title: ULTRASOUND RIGHT UPPER EXTREMITY VEINS

technique.description: Ultrasound images of the right upper extremity veins acquired. Color and spectral Doppler images also acquired.

findings.deep: No thrombus in the right internal jugular, subclavian, axillary, and brachial veins.
findings.superficial: Left basilic and cephalic veins are compressible.

impression: No deep venous thrombis in the right upper extremity.
